We affirm that focusing on what is beloved and inspired users would eventually raise the quality of both contents and the life of its creator.

-Paras

I considered fleeing to a remote island for a few weeks but realized I wasnt craving physical escape. I didnt actually want to be alone. I just wanted to be mentally free of obligations, most of which asserted themselves in a digital fashion.

-Baratunde Thurston, after his 25-day digital detox
